decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing Goblins with aggressive tendencies to quickly overwhelm the opponent. It includes cards like Aether Vial and Conspicuous Snoop to cheat out Goblins and generate card advantage. It also has cards like Putrid Goblin and Sling-Gang Lieutenant for sacrifice synergies. The deck utilizes Goblin Ringleader and Boggart Harbinger to search for specific Goblins and maintain card advantage. With cards like Kiki-Jiki, Mirror Breaker and Pashalik Mons, it has access to powerful combo plays. The deck aims to establish a strong board presence and pressure the opponent early on.

The deck revolves around using creatures with strong enters-the-battlefield effects and sacrificing them to tutor for specific creatures to create a powerful board state. It aims to quickly assemble a combination of creatures to overwhelm the opponent and win the game through synergistic interactions and a variety of toolbox options. The deck utilizes cards like Chord of Calling and Eldritch Evolution to search for key creatures like Yawgmoth, Thran Physician and Grist, the Hunger Tide to create a strong presence on the battlefield while controlling the opponent's board.
